<p source="SHANGBO.KONGZIJIANJIHUANZI 6.31.1 (STRIPS 1, 4, 20, 3) MACHENGYUAN 6: 199, 202, 218, 200 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-1a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-1a.1">子見季桓子.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-1a.2">[桓子] 曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-1a.3">“斯聞之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-1a.4">蓋賢者是能親 【1】仁,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-1a.5">親仁者是能行聖人之 道."</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-1a.6">"如夫親仁,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-1a.7">行聖人之道,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-1a.8">則斯【4】不足,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-1a.9">豈敢望之?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-1a.10">如夫見人不厭,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-1a.11">問禮不倦,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-1a.12">則【20】斯中心樂之.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.KONGZIJIANJIHUANZI 6.31.2 (STRIPS 3, 24, 16) MACHENGYUAN 6: 200, 222, 214 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-2a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-2a.1">夫子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-2a.2">“上不親仁,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-2a.3">而附富,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-2a.4">聞其詞於逸人乎?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-2a.5">夫士, 品物【3】不窮,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-2a.6">君子流其 觀焉.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-2a.7">品物備矣,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-2a.8">而亡成德 [...]【24】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-2a.9">[...] 者也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-2a.10">如此者,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-2a.11">焉與之處</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-2a.12">而察問其所學.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.KONGZIJIANJIHUANZI 6.31.3 (STRIPS 16, 6, 10, 8) MACHENGYUAN 6: 214, 204, 208, 207 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-3a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-3a.1">先【16】[...] 由仁歟?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-3a.2">蓋君子聽之.”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-3a.3">桓子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-3a.4">“如夫仁人之未察,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-3a.5">其行【6】 處可名而知歟?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-3a.6">夫子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-3a.7">“吾聞之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-3a.8">唯仁人[...]【10】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-3a.9">[...] 也.[...]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-3a.10">[...]有此貌也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-3a.11">而無以合諸此矣.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-3a.12">雖非仁人也,乃 [...]【8】</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.KONGZIJIANJIHUANZI 6.31.4 (STRIP 12) MACHENGYUAN 6: 210 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-4a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-4a.1">[...] 其物.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-4a.2">邪偽之民,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-4a.3">亦以其物.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-4a.4">審二道者以觀於民,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-4a.5">雖有[.] (過?)弗遠【12】 矣.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.KONGZIJIANJIHUANZI 6.31.5 (STRIPS 2, 7) MACHENGYUAN 6: 199, 205 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-5a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-5a.1">桓子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-5a.2">“二道者,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-5a.3">可得聞歟?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-5a.4">夫子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-5a.5">“言即至矣,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-5a.6">雖【2】 吾子勿問,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-5a.7">固將以告.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.KONGZIJIANJIHUANZI 6.31.6 (STRIPS 7, 26, 14) MACHENGYUAN 6: 205, 224, 212 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-6a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-6a.1">[...] 仁人之道,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-6a.2">衣服必中,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-6a.3">容貌不求異於人,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-6a.4">不[...]【7】也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-6a.5">好睘隹聚 (?), [...] [?]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-6a.6">仰天而歎,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-6a.7">曰:[?]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-6a.8">不奉,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-6a.9">不味酒肉【26】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-6a.10">[...] 不食五穀,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-6a.11">擇處(?) 杆,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-6a.12">豈不難乎?</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.KONGZIJIANJIHUANZI 6.31.7 (STRIPS 14, 11, 22) MACHENGYUAN 6: 212, 209, 220 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-7a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-7a.1">抑邪民之行也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-7a.2">好美以爲 [...],</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-7a.3">【14】此與仁人二者也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-7a.4">夫邪偽之民,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-7a.5">其術多方.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-7a.6">如【11】 悉言之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-7a.7">則恐久吾子.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.KONGZIJIANJIHUANZI 6.31.8 (STRIPS 22, 19, 17) MACHENGYUAN 6: 220, 217, 215 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-8a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-8a.1">桓子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-8a.2">“斯不佞,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-8a.3">吾子悉言之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-8a.4">猶恐弗知,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-8a.5">況其如【22】 微言之乎?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-8a.6">夫子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-8a.7">“與邪偽之民,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-8a.8">衣服好[...] 【19】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-8a.9">[...]皆求異於人; [...]</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.KONGZIJIANJIHUANZI 6.31.9 (STRIPS 17, 18) MACHENGYUAN 6: 215, 217 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-9a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-9a.1">[...] 衛 (?),</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-9a.2">興道學淫;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-9a.3">言不當其所,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-9a.4">皆同其[...];</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-9a.5">此邪民也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-9a.6">【17】行年彌久 [?],</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-9a.7">聞教</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-9a.8">不察不依;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-9a.9">其行板[=反?]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-9a.10">恭哀與豊 (?)【18】</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.KONGZIJIANJIHUANZI 6.31.10 (STRIPS 13, 15) MACHENGYUAN 6: 211, 213 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-10a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-10a.1">[...] 兼;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-10a.2">此邪民也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-10a.3">色不樸,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-10a.4">出言不忌;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-10a.5">見於君子,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-10a.6">大爲毋攝(=整);</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-10a.7">此 邪民也.【13】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-10a.8">君子恒以衆福,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-10a.9">句拜四方之位以動.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-10a.10">君子之以其所XX?,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-10a.11">窺之以其所欲,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-10a.12">知不行矣.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.KONGZIJIANJIHUANZI 6.31.11 (STRIPS 15, 5) MACHENGYUAN 6: 213, 203 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-11a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-11a.1">[...]不 [?] 兼,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-11a.2">絕以爲己兼, ???</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-11a.3">此民[...],</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-11a.4">【15】爲信以事其上,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-11a.5">仁其如此也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-11a.6">上唯道智,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-11a.7">亡不亂矣.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-11a.8">是故吾道之</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-11a.9">君子行,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-11a.10">冠弗見也;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-11a.11">語</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-11a.12">僉弗見也;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-11a.13">吾,[?]弗見也.[...]【5】</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.KONGZIJIANJIHUANZI 6.31.12 (STRIPS 27, 9) MACHENGYUAN 6: 225, 207 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-12a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-12a.1">是察,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-12a.2">求之於中.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-12a.3">此以不惑,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-12a.4">而民道之.【27】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-12a.5">仁援仁而進之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-12a.6">不仁人弗得進矣.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-12a.7">始得不可人而與 【9】</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.KONGZIJIANJIHUANZI 6.31.13 (STRIPS 21, 23) MACHENGYUAN 6: 219, 224 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-13a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-13a.1">[...] 者,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-13a.2">君子而立師保,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-13a.3">慎其禮樂,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-13a.4">道其 【21】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-13a.5">[...] 君子有道,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0060_tls_001-13a.6">生民之化 【23】</seg>
                </p>

</div>
